subject: Soccer
lead_paragraph: Peter Crouch’s goal with 10 minutes left gave Tottenham Hotspur a 1-0 victory at the Serie A leader, A.C. Milan, in the first leg of their Champions League Round of 16 matchup on Tuesday.
